.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, dunhill, ritmeester
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, climbing, snowboarding
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | chaman        | ritmeester  | oliveros       |
| Sport         | badminton | climbing    | biathlon | snowboarding |

