.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, mystery, romance
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | mystery | romance | adventure        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

