.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, photographer, social-worker, videographer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, blend, chaman
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the dannemann-smoker is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the blend-smoker is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | bartender  | videographer | photographer  | social-worker |
| Cigar       | blend | baccarat        | chaman | dannemann       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

