4. the japanese is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the colombian is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the japanese is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the colombian is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Nationality         | mexican   | colombian | japanese | pakistani  |

