.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, bartender, lawyer, scientist
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, january, may
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, french, mexican
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the french##1
2. the bartender is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is the chinese##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the mexican##1
7. the french is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | lawyer  | architect | bartender  | scientist |
| Birthday   | january    | july       | march | may      |
| Nationality   | chinese | canadian  | mexican    | french    |

