.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, mexican, russian
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, billiard, canasta
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the british##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | british | indonesian | mexican | russian |
| Game         | go | monopoly | canasta  | billiard  |
| Transport     | roller  | snowmobile | van     | subway  |

